Title: Minha filha Margot
DateModified: '2019-02-13'
DatePublished: '2019-02-13'
Url: https://www.worldnomads.com/create/scholarships/writing/2019/applications/minha-filha-margot
SetInCountry: Portugal
Category: Making a local connection
AuthorName: Aexandre Lima
AuthorCountry: Brazil
Text: Talks about a father who due to the political situation of his country (Brazil)
  goes to Portugal with his daughter, but he is very attached to his culture, and
  his daughter as a little girl quickly adopts Portuguese habits, including the child
  who is beginning to speak begins by speaking with the Portuguese accent, but the
  father tris to keep the memory and the culture of his home with him and teach his
  dougther the culture where they come from
